OL,3,CTicket sales open for Barbie
OL,4,Cexhibition coming to Scotland for
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FTickets are due to go on sale for an
OL,8,Fexhibition charting the evolution of
OL,9,FBarbie which is coming to Scotland for
OL,10,Fthe first time.
OL,12,FA rare, hand-painted first edition
OL,13,FBarbie is among the objects which will
OL,14,Fbe on display at the show at
OL,15,FKelvingrove Art Gallery and Museum in
OL,16,FGlasgow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
