OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773716599
OL,3,CTicket sales open for Barbie
OL,4,Cexhibition coming to Scotland for
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FBarbie: The Exhibition explores the
OL,8,Fhistory of the doll from 1959 to the
OL,9,Fpresent day and features items
OL,10,Fincluding clothes, playsets and
OL,11,Fvehicles.
OL,13,FThere will be more than 150 dolls on
OL,14,Fshow, including the first black,
OL,15,FHispanic and Asian versions, as well
OL,16,Fas the first Barbie with Down's
OL,17,FSyndrome and the first in a wheelchair.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
