OL,3,CTicket sales open for Barbie
OL,4,Cexhibition coming to Scotland for
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FTickets for the exhibition, a
OL,8,Fpartnership between the Design Museum
OL,9,Fin London and Mattel Inc, go on sale
OL,10,Fat 10am on Tuesday.
OL,12,FBailie Annette Christie, chair of
OL,13,FGlasgow Life, which runs Kelvingrove
OL,14,FArt Gallery and Museum, said: "Now
OL,15,Fspring has sprung and the days are
OL,16,Fgetting longer, it's a joy to start
OL,17,Fplanning the adventures ahead this
OL,18,Fsummer.
OL,26,@vD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
