PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773716599
OL,3,CTicket sales open for Barbie
OL,4,Cexhibition coming to Scotland for
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,F"This year, that includes the
OL,8,Fopportunity to discover the history
OL,9,Fand design of the doll that started it
OL,10,Fall, the phenomenon that is Barbie.
OL,12,F"Glasgow Life is excited to work with
OL,13,Fthe Design Museum and Mattel to bring
OL,14,Fan enduring icon to Glasgow.
OL,16,F"This exhibition is stylish,
OL,17,Fculturally significant and rooted in
OL,18,Fdesign history and it's an honour to
OL,19,Fbe the first city in Scotland to host
OL,20,Fa major exhibition dedicated to Barbie.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
