SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773716599
OL,3,CTicket sales open for Barbie
OL,4,Cexhibition coming to Scotland for
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,F"With tickets on sale, now is the
OL,8,Fperfect time to get ahead of the crowd
OL,9,Fand plan a joyful, engaging, even
OL,10,Fnostalgic visit with family and
OL,11,Ffriends.
OL,13,F"Make a real day of it at what
OL,14,Fpromises to be one of the biggest and
OL,15,Fmost talked-about shows of the summer."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@gO]
