PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773716599
OL,3,CTicket sales open for Barbie
OL,4,Cexhibition coming to Scotland for
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FOther highlights of the show include
OL,8,Fsome of the most popular dolls over
OL,9,Fthe decades ranging from the 1971
OL,10,FSunset Malibu Barbie to the 1985 Day
OL,11,Fto Night Barbie, whose pink work suit
OL,12,Fcould be transformed into an evening
OL,13,Fgown.
OL,15,FAlso on show will be two examples of
OL,16,F1992's Totally Hair Barbie, whose long
OL,17,Fhair reached all the way to her toes.
OL,19,FRare Barbie Dreamhouses, vehicles and
OL,20,Faccessories will also be on show.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
