FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773716599
OL,3,CTicket sales open for Barbie
OL,4,Cexhibition coming to Scotland for
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FMany of Barbie's friends also feature
OL,8,Fin the exhibition, including a section
OL,9,Fdedicated to Ken which explores how he
OL,10,Fhas evolved since he made his debut in
OL,11,F1961.
OL,13,FThe exhibition opens at Kelvingrove
OL,14,FArt Gallery and Museum on June 13 2026
OL,15,Fand runs until October 18 this year.
OL,17,FTickets can be bought online at
OL,18,Fwww.glasgowlife.org.uk/barbie
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
